                                        "text": "Mounting is simple (bondic glue, or clamp from two sides) and the sample holder sits very nicely in place with magnets."
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Extremely easy to find the sample using a pre-scan and then a 3D pre-scan to work out the extents of the lateral tiling you should do. "
