                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Software is a little buggy when it comes to prescan and positioning of the final acquisition, i.e. define it in one place, but it starts imaging in another - they are aware and are very open to feedback and making changes. NOTE: this doesn't always happen"
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Open-top reservoir is a little prone to spillage"
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Glass coverslip sits on top of reservoir and if you get medium on it, it needs cleaning, which takes time and can be frustrating"
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Need to re-calibrate the SLM every time you want to acquire images at a different zoom or refractive index. I.e. there is no way to save these files for each combo and just load up a previous file from a previous SLM calibration - they will work on this, I'm sure"
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "rich_text_section",
                                "elements": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "No user config files saved for the software, so can't save settings for an acquisition to return to the next day"
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ],
                        "style": "bullet",
                        "indent": 0,
                        "border": 0
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\nThere are probably more, happy to show it\/talk about it to anyone who wants to see it, by Zoom or in person."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
